{
  "text": "This completes the proof of Theorem 3.3. [CITATION_1] , the initial condition of blow-up mechanism is 4|µ 0 | ≤ µ 1 . Therefore, Theorem 3.3 improves the blow-up result in [CITATION_2] .",
